Wow last night I took my family out to celebrate after the A level exams and I also caught up with the amazing @nancysilverton ( I love her ) at her New @pizzeriamozzalondon  the food was so good ! definitely some of the best pizza in London ..thoughtfully made dough, wood oven  great ingredients great service home made ice cream !! Come on man this is simple food done good… without question I would recommend this restaurant for a premo elegant pizza night out we had a ball !!! Thank you Nancy and chef @zallen77 xx and thank you @clerkenwellboyec1 for taking the shots xxx
